'''Hon. Béata Habyarimana''' ni [[Rwanda|umunyarwandakazi]] ndetse n’umucuruzi w'umunyamwuga mu bijyanye n’imicungire y’imari akaba n’umunyapolitiki ni Minisitiri w’ubucuruzi n’inganda muri guverinoma [[Inama y’Abaminisitiri|y’abaminisitiri]], kuva ku ya 15 Werurwe 2021.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/who-are-new-ministers-and-provincial-governors</ref><ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/new-trade-minister-prioritise-sme-growth</ref>

== Amashuri ==
Hon. Habyarimana yakurikiranye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bijyanye n'imari n’ubukungu.muri kaminuza y'u Rwanda kuva 1996 kugeza 2000, kandi afite impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya kabiri cya Masters mu miyoborere mu by’imari yakuye muri Kaminuza ya Maastricht mu Buholandi. Yayibonye hagati y’umwaka wa 2009 na 2011.<ref>https://www.webrwanda.com/2021/03/imbamutima-za-gasana-gatabazi-soraya.html</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Beata ni umuhanga mu bukungu ufite uburambe bwimyaka irenga 15 mu bijyanye n’imari kuko mbere yuko ashyirwaho yakoraga nk'umuyobozi wungirije muri Banki ya Afurika.<ref>http://apanews.net/en/pays/rwanda/news/kagame-appoints-new-trade-minister-in-mild-cabinet-reshuffle</ref> Yakoraga kandi nk'umuyobozi mukuru muri Agaseke Bank , Yakoze muri Banki y'abaturage y'u  Rwanda (BPR) mu myanya ikomeye. Yabanje kandi gukorana na Bill na Melinda Gates Foundation.<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/umunyakuri-wakabije-inzozi-iby-igitabo-cyamuhinduye-byinshi-ku-buzima-bwa</ref>

